        <p class="csf-hero__body">CAST Design Fireplaces has been designing, building, and installing custom cast stone fireplaces across <a href="/service-areas/dallas">Dallas</a>, <a href="/service-areas/fort-worth">Fort Worth</a>, and the DFW metroplex for over 20 years. We work with a single family of materials — premium cast stone — and we've mastered it completely.</p>
