        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WHY CAST STONE ═══ -->
  <section class="csf-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="csf-section__label">Why Cast Stone</p>
      <h2>Why Homeowners Choose Cast Stone Fireplaces</h2>
      <p class="csf-section__intro">Over 20+ years of installing fireplaces across the DFW area, we've had thousands of conversations with homeowners about materials. Here's what they consistently love about cast stone:</p>
      <div class="csf-benefits">
        <div class="csf-benefit">
          <div class="csf-benefit__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>The Look of Limestone. The Durability of Modern Craftsmanship.</h3>
          <p>Cast stone captures the warm, organic character of natural limestone — the subtle texture, the soft color variation, the sense of permanence — without limestone's inconsistencies. Every profile, every curve, every corbel detail is exactly what you designed it to be.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="csf-benefit">
          <div class="csf-benefit__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.53 16.122a3 3 0 00-5.78 1.128 2.25 2.25 0 01-2.4 2.245 4.5 4.5 0 008.4-2.245c0-.399-.078-.78-.22-1.128zm0 0a15.998 15.998 0 003.388-1.62m-5.043-.025a15.994 15.994 0 011.622-3.395m3.42 3.42a15.995 15.995 0 004.764-4.648l3.876-5.814a1.151 1.151 0 00-1.597-1.597L14.146 6.32a15.996 15.996 0 00-4.649 4.763m3.42 3.42a6.776 6.776 0 00-3.42-3.42" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Fully Custom to Your Home</h3>
          <p>Unlike off-the-shelf fireplace surrounds, a CAST Design fireplace is designed around your specific space. We account for ceiling height, room scale, architectural style, and your personal taste. No catalog browsing, no compromises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="csf-benefit">
          <div class="csf-benefit__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386l-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364l-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227l-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Ideal for the Texas Climate</h3>
          <p>Our cast stone mix is engineered for the DFW environment — expansion, contraction, humidity — without losing dimensional stability or finish integrity over time. It performs in Texas summers the same way it performs on a cold January evening.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="csf-benefit">
          <div class="csf-benefit__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>A Fraction of the Cost of Carved Natural Stone</h3>
          <p>Custom hand-carved limestone or marble fireplaces command extraordinary prices. Cast stone delivers the same presence, the same weight, the same elegance — at a cost that makes genuine craftsmanship accessible to a far wider range of DFW homes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="csf-benefit">
          <div class="csf-benefit__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 011.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 00.475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 00-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 01-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.563.563 0 00-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 01-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 00-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.563.563 0 01.321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 00.475-.345L11.48 3.5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Fireplace or Showpiece</h3>
          <p>Many of our clients use their cast stone fireplaces as the central design element of an entire room renovation. The fireplace becomes the anchor — and everything else in the room is chosen to complement it. That kind of visual gravity is difficult to achieve with any other material.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ PRODUCTS ═══ -->
  <section class="csf-section csf-section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="csf-section__label">Our Collection</p>
      <h2>Our Cast Stone Fireplace Collection</h2>
      <p class="csf-section__intro">We design and build every piece in-house at our DFW facility. Our cast stone fireplace offerings include:</p>
      <div class="csf-products">
        <div class="csf-product">
          <h3>Cast Stone Fireplace Mantels</h3>
          <p>The mantel is the crown of any fireplace — the piece that commands attention and sets the tone for the room. Our mantels range from understated and linear to ornately carved traditional designs. Every profile is available in custom widths and heights to fit your firebox exactly.</p>
          <a href="/gallery" class="csf-product__link">View Mantel Gallery →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="csf-product">
          <h3>Cast Stone Fireplace Surrounds</h3>
          <p>A full fireplace surround — encompassing the mantel shelf, legs, frieze, and hearth — creates a complete architectural frame for your firebox. Our surrounds are designed as cohesive compositions, not assembled from unrelated parts.</p>
          <a href="/gallery" class="csf-product__link">View Surround Gallery →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="csf-product">
          <h3>Outdoor Cast Stone Fireplaces</h3>
          <p>Texas outdoor living is year-round, and a cast stone outdoor fireplace is the element that transforms a patio into a true gathering place. We design and install outdoor fireplaces that hold up beautifully to the weather and look at home in the landscape.</p>
          <a href="/gallery" class="csf-product__link">View Outdoor Gallery →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="csf-product">
          <h3>Custom Range Hoods in Cast Stone</h3>
          <p>For clients who want architectural continuity throughout their home, we also design <a href="/products/range-hoods">cast stone range hoods</a> that echo the language of their fireplace — the same profiles, the same textures, the same craftsmanship.</p>
          <a href="/products/range-hoods" class="csf-product__link">Learn About Range Hoods →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

